H. C. JONES, Individually and as Collector of Internal Revenue, v. WETHERBEE ELECTRIC COMPANY. No. 3589. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Nov. 3, 1947. Robert E. Shelton, U. S. Atty., of Oklahoma City, Okl.,. for appellant. Mosteller & McElroy, of Oklahoma City, Okl., for appellee.

Before PHILLIPS, Circuit Judge, and SYMES, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Docketed and dismissed per stipulation.
